274
00:19:48,083 --> 00:19:49,376
[sobs]

275
00:19:51,128 --> 00:19:52,129
[sniffles]

276
00:19:52,213 --> 00:19:54,924
We need to find those two
or who knows what they'll do...

277
00:19:55,508 --> 00:20:01,347
THE ANNUAL HIKARI CITY YAGIBUSHI FESTIVAL
LIVE BROADCASTING

278
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:03,057
[reporter] Hello, ladies and gentlemen!

279
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:06,894
We're coming to you live from
the Yagibushi Festival once again!

280
00:20:06,977 --> 00:20:08,562
[all laughing]

281
00:20:08,646 --> 00:20:12,691
There are so many people here already,
and the place is filled with excitement.

282
00:20:12,775 --> 00:20:14,777
[indistinct chatter]

283
00:20:26,747 --> 00:20:29,124
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

284
00:20:38,759 --> 00:20:40,094
The summer festival?

285
00:20:40,678 --> 00:20:41,679
What?

286
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:46,016
It was marked in the calendar
in Sawa's room.

287
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:47,101
FESTIVAL

288
00:20:47,184 --> 00:20:49,520
She's never cared
about the festival before...

289
00:20:56,068 --> 00:20:57,361
Ma'am!

290
00:20:58,904 --> 00:21:00,823
[indistinct chatter]

291
00:21:04,034 --> 00:21:06,996
[men singing]

292
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:10,040
HIKARI YAGIBUSHI

293
00:21:13,711 --> 00:21:15,129
[food sizzling]

294
00:21:21,343 --> 00:21:25,014
KEROSENE

295
00:21:36,692 --> 00:21:37,693
[gun fires]

296
00:21:37,776 --> 00:21:39,737
[Yamada] No way! That should've gone down!

297
00:21:39,820 --> 00:21:42,031
-That's not right.
-[Kojima] It's karma.

298
00:21:42,114 --> 00:21:43,324
-[Ai] Yamada...
-[Yamada] Huh?

299
00:21:44,199 --> 00:21:45,492
Have you seen Kasuga?

300
00:21:45,576 --> 00:21:47,453
What? He's here?

301
00:21:47,536 --> 00:21:48,537
No clue.

302
00:21:49,079 --> 00:21:50,164
[woman screaming]

303
00:21:56,337 --> 00:21:57,922
[indistinct chatter]

304
00:21:59,423 --> 00:22:01,800
Excuse me! Sorry!

305
00:22:02,551 --> 00:22:04,219
[man 1] Run, get away! Hurry!

306
00:22:07,389 --> 00:22:12,144
-[man 2] It's not safe! Please get back!
-[man 3] Get away from the bandstand!

307
00:22:15,481 --> 00:22:16,732
[reporter] We have an emergency!

308
00:22:16,815 --> 00:22:20,444
Suspicious individuals with knives
are on the festival platform!

309
00:22:20,527 --> 00:22:24,073
It appears nobody has been injured.
I repeat!

310
00:22:24,156 --> 00:22:27,409
Suspicious individuals with knives
are on the festival platform!

311
00:22:27,493 --> 00:22:29,912
People are panic-stricken!

312
00:22:30,996 --> 00:22:33,624
The two have taken their masks off!

313
00:22:33,707 --> 00:22:35,793
It's a boy and a girl!

314
00:22:40,547 --> 00:22:42,091
[both] To the shit bugs!

315
00:22:42,174 --> 00:22:45,219
To all the shit bugs of this town!

316
00:22:48,597 --> 00:22:50,891
TO BE CONTINUED

317
00:22:50,975 --> 00:22:53,852
[♪ closing theme music playing]

318
00:23:48,032 --> 00:23:49,033
ON THE NEXT EPISODE

319
00:23:49,116 --> 00:23:51,744
[narrator] Kasuga and Nakamura
take their biggest stage

320
00:23:51,827 --> 00:23:54,997
as shit bugs surround them.

321
00:23:55,080 --> 00:23:56,707
Next, on episode eight,

322
00:23:57,541 --> 00:24:00,836
will the young two be able
to reach the other side?

323
00:24:00,919 --> 00:24:02,963
Translated by Yuka Kristi

